item.description:
Due to a lack of interest and commitment this Meetup has been canceled. Please feel free to participate in the Walk on your own as I am doing. I will be leaving at 7 am with other people. Please contact me if you would like to sponsor/donate to the cause.

The Project Bread Walk for Hunger is Sunday, May 2.

Are you prepared to walk up to 20 miles, make a donation and raise some money?

Please check out the Project Bread web site for more details.

If you are definitely ready to go at 7 am on May 2, please RSVP yes by Sunday, March 21.

If we have a Native quorum by next Sunday, we will register and do it.
item.how_to_find_us: Meet 7 am at the Registration Table Boston Common
item.name: Project Bread Walk for Hunger
